title.rendered: Exeter Outdoor Dining Set – solid wood

content.rendered:
*Currently on special offer until 31st May 2023, until stocks last* *Normally £991.8 each *

The Exeter Dining Set features a square table and four chairs in a varnished softwood. 

The Exeter Dining Set is strong, durable, easy to maintain and easy to clean.

It does well in heavily used, outdoor areas and has a 40mm diameter hole in the centre of the table for a parasol.

Perfect for hospitality venues including pubs, hotels, bars and restaurants.

Dimensions in mm

– Chair: 840 H x 380 W x 320 D x 460 Seat Height x 5.7KG

– Table: 720 H x 900 W x 900 D x 17.7KG

12 month warranty. May need some self assembly.
